reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great packing cubes
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these cubes for my hard sided suitcase. One side has a zippered topper but one side only has an elastic band and all of my clothes were always askew when I would open the suitcase up. These cubes are great for keeping my items organized! Love them!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They do as advertised
reviews.reviewText: They were promptly delivered. A nice variety of sizes. Zippers are light weight but should be fine just don’t over stuff. I like the tie down straps in the larger bags.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I like the color, the quality feels stronger than other brands. I would suggest to stamp what is for in each bag, but I understand in the end, is the person who will decide how they will use it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Will never pack normal again!
reviews.reviewText: I can't believe I haven't had these in all my years of travel! These really cut down on the amount of space that clothes take up when you don't use them! I can pack the same amount in a carry on size suitcase using these cubes than I can NOT using them and needed a bigger suitcase. I've gifted these several times to family and friends and have never heard of complaints!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful grey set. All of them fits in my suitcase nicely and makes organizing my bag much easier. When I'm using my weekender bag I can fit 5 plus my large roll up cosmetic bag another company. Definitely would recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Held up to 2 months of intense backpack travel... but not much more
reviews.reviewText: Bought these last minute to have something before I headed out for a 2 month backpacking trip. While I'm happy to report all of these made it through the trip in tact (which is a feat given the amount I can wrench down on those zippers); the bags were worse for wear by the time I returned home. Surprisingly the biggest issue with the cubes are the hemmed seams, which seemed to come apart on almost every bag after about 2-3 weeks.

reviews.reviewText: It is useful for packing 10 to 15 days of clothes easily, we organize day wise clothes into different cubes and it was easy to use and assemble it across the trip.
